## 一维前缀和

`pre[]`用于计算前缀和，`a[]`为原数组

```cpp
初始化: pre[i] = pre[i - 1] + a[i];
pre[r] - pre[l-1] 为 a[l..r]的和
pre[i] 表示 a[1..i] 的和
```
---
### 示例程序
```cpp
#include <iostream>
#include <cstring>
#include <cstdlib>
#include <cstdio>
using namespace std;
#define MAX 10000

int a[MAX], pre[MAX] = {0};
int n, l, r;

int main()
{
    cout << "How many numbers? ";
    cin >> n;
    cout << "Enter " << n << " numbers:" << endl;
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
    {
        cin >> a[i];
        pre[i] = pre[i - 1] + a[i];
    }
    cout << "From ";    cin >> l;
    cout << "To ";      cin >> r;

    cout << "a[" << l << ".." << r << "]=";
    cout << pre[r] - pre[l - 1] << endl;
    return 0;
}
```
运行结果
```cpp
How many numbers? 10
Enter 10 numbers:
123 123 5 34 354 -12 54 -21 0 21
From 3
To 8
a[3..8]=414
```

